    <h1>Overview of Verbs</h1>
    <p> Welcome to the Overview!<br>
      <br>
      Here you will be able to review basic grammar concepts that will help you know how each verb should be conjugated
      and what that will look like. In French, unlike English, all verbs are conjugated according to who the subject is,
      whether they are male or female, how many people are doing the action, and occasionally, also who or what the action is happening to.
      <br><br> Click one of the following categories to learn more about
      how to conjugate French verbs!
    </p>
