    <h3> Regular IR Verbs </h3>
      <p> Similar to the ER verbs, regular IR verbs drop their "<em>-ir</em>" endings and add new ones depending on what person they are in.
          The endings look different, but they function in the same way. <br><br>
          Check out the examples below of two IR verbs in the present tense to see how they look:
      </p>
      <div class="example">
