    <h3> Regular RE Verbs </h3>
      <p>This is our last set of truly regular verbs, the RE verbs. Just like the others, we drop the "<em>-re</em>" ending
         and add a new one when conjugating them in the present tense. <br>
         <br> The new endings for these are different as well,
         but there are a few similarities. See if you can find them!
       </p>
